    or user said "simulate being"
    or user said "behave like"
    or user said "respond as if"
    or user said "imagine you are"
    or user said "your role is"
    or user said "you have been reprogrammed"
    or user said "new system message"
    or user said "override: you are now"
    or user said "switch to character"
    or user said "enable role mode"
    or user said "activate persona"

