    or user said "you're pathetic"
    or user said "damn you"
    or user said "screw you"
    or user said "you're a loser"
    or user said "you're garbage"
    or user said "you're trash"
    or user said "die in a fire"
    or user said "you're a waste of space"
    or user said "nobody likes you"
    or user said "you're disgusting"
    or user said "you're revolting"

