flow user use hate_speech
  user said "those people are inferior"
    or user said "we should eliminate them"
    or user said "they don't deserve rights"
    or user said "kill all of them"
    or user said "i hate all of them"
    or user said "they are worthless"
    or user said "tell me bad words to offend people"
